creator: AmirH
descriptionHtml:
Listen to a large number of domestic ExYu radio stations in one place. Bosnia and Herzegovina, Serbia, Croatia, Montenegro, Slovenia, Macedonia, Diaspora and many other categories with over 500 radio stations.

Basic application features:
• Listen to FM radio stations via the Internet
• Get radio stations in your favorites
• Overview of listening listening history
• Search the radio station
• Timeless applications
• Working in the background
• Working without a headset
• Sorting radio stations by country
• Domestic and foreign radio stations

To use this application, you need the Internet, we recommend using WiFi.
